Dry yourself first.

84
00:08:14,577 --> 00:08:16,496
Give me your clothes. I hate dinosaurs.

85
00:08:20,583 --> 00:08:21,959
This is fascinating.

86
00:08:22,126 --> 00:08:24,253
You can take care of all your needs here,

87
00:08:24,337 --> 00:08:26,297
